data.description: Welcome to your dream condo in the heart of Great Neck, Virginia Beach! This stunning property offers the perfect blend of convenience, comfort, and style. As you step inside, you're greeted by an open floor concept that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it ideal for entertaining guests or simply enjoying everyday living. Feat. two primary ensuites. New Windows w/ lifetime warranty. New HVAC. New carpet upstairs. Updated Kitchen. All Appliances Convey. New washer/dryer. Turf patio. Condo fees incl. water/sewage, master insurance, ground maint., & pool. 15 min to chicks beach, 10 min. to ocean front! Great local restaurants & neighborhood parks!!
